OL,5, A funeral home director in the US state
OL,6, of Indiana, where the decomposing      
OL,7, bodies of more than 31 people were     
OL,8, found, has plead guilty to more than 40
OL,9, counts of felony theft.                
OL,11,FProsecutors charged Randy Lankford, who
OL,12,Fowns the Jeffersonville business, for  
OL,13,Ffailing to complete the funeral        
OL,14,Fservices he was paid for.              
OL,16,FThe judge suggested he may serve 12    
OL,17,Fyears and must also compensate 53      
OL,18,Ffamilies $46,000 (#37,000) in total.   
OL,20,FLankford will be sentenced in June.    
